    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1925-06-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1925-06-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="47"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d47">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A14/336: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Burton</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, [<date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-06-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 17, 1925</hi>—(<hi rend="italic">?</hi>) <hi
                                rend="italic">p.m.</hi>]</date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 17—10:30 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>90. Gibson and I signed convention, final act, protocol of signature and gas
                    protocol at 12 noon. Did not sign final declaration.<note n="60"
                        xml:id="d47fn60">i. e., Declaration Regarding the Territory of Ifni; see
                        footnote 63, <ref target="#pg_60">p. 60</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Burton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
